---
import Layout from '../../Base.astro';
import SimpleHero from '../../components/SimpleHero.astro';
import FeaturedArticles from "../../components/FeaturedArticles.astro";
import ServicesRelatedWork from "../../components/ServicesRelatedWork.astro";
import "../../styles/pages/_services-list.scss";

---

<Layout
	title='Copywriting services | Florida Marketing Agency'
	description='When your business knows what it does but customers still do not get it, the problem is usually the words. We write copy that makes the offer clear, builds trust, and gives people a reason to move.'
>
	<SimpleHero tagline='Marketing & Messaging Services' title='Copywriting' description="When your business knows what it does but customers still do not get it, the problem is usually the words. We write copy that makes the offer clear, builds trust, and gives people a reason to move." lottieFile='copywriting.json' />
	<div class='service-body'>
		<div class='wrapper wrapper--narrow'>
			<h2>Where teams get stuck</h2>
			<p>
				Many businesses know their offer inside and out, but that clarity never makes it onto the page. Website copy gets vague, ads sound interchangeable, and sales material asks the customer to do too much work.
			</p>
			<p>When the message is unclear, the audience leaves with questions instead of confidence.</p>
			<h2>How we fix it</h2>
			<p>We start by understanding the audience, the offer, and the context the copy needs to support. Then we turn subject-matter expertise into writing that is easier to follow and easier to act on.</p>
			<ul>
				<li>Website pages and hero sections</li>
				<li>Product and service descriptions</li>
				<li>Case studies and about pages</li>
				<li>Blog Articles</li>
				<li>Ad headlines and campaign copy</li>
				<li>Social Media Posts</li>
				<li>Brochures, postcards, posters, and other marketing collateral</li>
			</ul>
			<p>For website projects, that usually means starting with a sitemap and content plan so we know what each page needs to say, in what order, and for whom. For campaigns or collateral, we focus on the goal of the piece and the response it needs to generate.</p>
			<h2>What moving forward looks like</h2>
			<p>If you are launching a site, tightening campaign messaging, or rewriting material that no longer reflects the business, we can help identify the pages and messages that matter most and write them in the right order.</p>
			<p><a href='/contact/' class='button button--green'>Talk Through Your Messaging</a></p>
		</div>
		<ServicesRelatedWork tag={70} />
	</div>
	<FeaturedArticles />
</Layout>
